  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "Boss, the Minnesota Tribe took the Abyss design and rebuilt it with everything they could get their hands on. Clan engine, Clan PPC, Angel ECM, Artemis V, CASE II, jump jets. They only gave it to their best, so every time one showed up on a Clan homeworld, people paid attention. Getting one of these in our bay is something else. This is not a mech you put a rookie in.",
